###

### Get all students
GET {{VNX.API_HostAddress}}/api/student
Accept: application/json

###

### Get student by id
GET {{VNX.API_HostAddress}}/api/student/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create student
POST {{VNX.API_HostAddress}}/api/student
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentCode": "S12345",
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phone": "1234567890",
  "dateOfBirth": "2000-01-01T00:00:00",
  "address": "123 Main St",
  "campusId": 1,
  "departmentId": 1,
  "courseId": 1,
  "batch": "2022-2026",
  "admissionDate": "2022-01-01T00:00:00",
  "status": "Active",
  "guardianName": "Jane Doe",
  "guardianPhone": "0987654321",
  "guardianEmail": "jane.doe@example.com"
}

